No. 509,

October Term, 1962.

Reed v. The Yaka et al., Vernon S. Jones, James B. Magnor, J. Ward O’Neill, Mahlon Dickerson, J. Stewart Harrison, Scott H. Elder and Gilbert R. Johnson for American Marine Institute, Inc., et al.

373 U. S. 410. The motion of American Marine Institute, Inc., et al. for leave to file a brief, as amici curiae, is granted. Petition for rehearing denied.
